    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-tomato-and-basil-soup-with-mozzarella-and-pesto-toastie/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella </strong>into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-tomato-and-basil-soup-with-mozzarella-and-pesto-toastie/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>torn mozzarella</strong> to a medium bowl with your <strong>traditional Italian pesto</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until completely combined \u2013 this is your <strong>mozzarella & pesto filling</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-tomato-and-basil-soup-with-mozzarella-and-pesto-toastie/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Divide the <strong>mozzarella & pesto filling</strong> between the<strong> ciabatta base[s] </strong>and<strong> </strong>spread almost to the edges, leaving a small border</p><p>Top with a<strong> ciabatta lid</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>mozzarella & pesto toastie[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-tomato-and-basil-soup-with-mozzarella-and-pesto-toastie/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-tomato-and-basil-soup-with-mozzarella-and-pesto-toastie/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the<strong> mozzarella & pesto toastie[s] </strong>and cover with a smaller pan</p><p>Add a heavy weight (e.g. several tins) to the top pan and cook for 3-4 min per side, checking occasionally or until the ciabatta is golden and the cheese has melted</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 5? Use 2 pans or you may need to do this in batches!</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-tomato-and-basil-soup-with-mozzarella-and-pesto-toastie/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat your <strong>RE:NOURISH tomato soup </strong>according to the pack instructions</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/re-nourish-tomato-and-basil-soup-with-mozzarella-and-pesto-toastie/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>RE:NOURISH tomato soup </strong>in a bowl with your <strong>mozzarella & pesto toastie </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
